'''HMS ''Revenge'' (S27)''' was the fourth of the [[Royal Navy]]'s [[Resolution class submarine|''Resolution''-class]] [[ballistic missile]] [[submarine]]s.

Built by [[Cammell Laird]] and launched on [[15 March]] [[1968]], she was marked for disposal in 1992.

